defaultThe amalgamation and integration of the services was
default&#xa0;
defaultbrought to Staffordshire County Council Assets and Budget Scrutiny Committee Integration of health and social care came about as a result of the creation of the Staffordshire and Stoke on Trent Partnership Trust.
