defaultScrutiny in Solihull MBC : The HCSB have received a number of reports on the way health and social care are working together through an ‘Accountable Care Partnership’ and will be monitoring the work, outcomes and efficiencies being progressed through a new integrated care project which has just been set up. (This work is being sponsored by the Health and Wellbeing Board)
